Package: SER
Type: Package
Title: Short-period Environmental Regime
Version: 0.1
Author: Kun Guo <kunguo16@gmail.com>, Naicheng Wu <naichengwu88@gmail.com>, and Tenna Riis <tenna.riis@bios.au.dk>
Maintainer: Kun Guo <kunguo16@gmail.com>
Description: 1. Currently, this package only contain 1 function, which can calculate short-period (day-, month-, or year- specific) environmental regime (SER).
    2. A tutorial is availiable for how short-period environmental regime is developed and how it can be applied for different types of data.
